Package it.polimi.ingsw.storage

Class ResourceManager

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.storage.ResourceManager
public class ResourceManager
extends java.lang.Object
This class let resource retrieval operations simpler since it encapsulates GSON logic and instantiate directly the class needed to perform a certain task.
Author:
AndreaAltomare
